name: First Floor
summary_text: Floor Nine comprises eight rooms, organized into living, sleeping, and utility zones to promote smooth flow between spaces. Living areas center a welcoming lounge and seating setup with TV stand, coffee table, and rug, plus a compact entry space anchored by a wall mirror and lighting. A sleeping zone features a bed, nightstands, and dresser, while utilities cover a western kitchen and small washroom. A central freestanding cabinet in the compact room adds storage, yielding a cohesive, neutral, functional layout.
